---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="About — Francesco Bozzo"
    description="Learn more about Francesco Bozzo"
>
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
        I'm Francesco Bozzo, a Software Development Engineer II at Amazon in
        Milan, Italy. I work in the Fulfillment Technologies organization
        focusing on optimizing container flow and routing across Amazon
        warehouses worldwide.
    </p>

    <p>
        Before Amazon, I was a Machine Learning Engineer at the Bruno Kessler
        Foundation in Trento, developing deep learning models for industrial
        equipment prognostics. I also worked with Wikipedia datasets at Eurecat
        to investigate contributor drop-off from the platform.
    </p>

    <p>
        I hold an MSc in Artificial Intelligence Systems and a BSc in Computer
        Science, both with maximum grade with honors from the University of
        Trento. My MSc thesis explored LLM-based planning for autonomous
        software agents.
    </p>

    <p>
        Outside work, I am passionate about Nix for managing my machines,
        including NixOS on my Strix Halo Framework Desktop and Nix Darwin on my
        MacBook. I self-host multiple services for managing documents, photos,
        DNS, search engine, home automation, monitoring and alerting, and
        especially serving local LLMs. I am also passionate about reverse
        engineering, which first introduced me to programming during high
        school. I focus on reverse engineering Nintendo DS games, especially to
        support fan translation projects.
    </p>

    <p class="cv-download">
        <a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="download-link">
            <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="16"
                height="16"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"
                ></path><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline><line
                    x1="12"
                    y1="15"
                    x2="12"
                    y2="3"></line></svg
            >
            Download Resume (PDF)
        </a>
    </p>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .cv-download {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 1.5em 0;
    }

    .download-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.4em;
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--color-accent);
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.4em 0.8em;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition:
            background var(--transition-fast),
            color var(--transition-fast);
    }

    .download-link:hover {
        background: var(--color-accent);
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
</style>
